---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { COMPANY_NAME, SITE_URL, SUPPORT_EMAIL } from '../lib/site';

const lastUpdated = '2026-01-21';
---

<Layout
	title="Privacy Policy"
	description="Privacy Policy for the Wean Nicotine iOS app."
	canonicalPath="/privacy"
>
	<section class="page">
		<div class="container prose">
			<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
			<p class="muted">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

			<h2>Who we are</h2>
			<p>
				This Privacy Policy applies to the Wean Nicotine iOS app (“Wean Nicotine”, “the app”). The data controller is
				<strong>{COMPANY_NAME}</strong>.
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Website: <a href={SITE_URL}>{SITE_URL}</a></li>
				<li>
					Contact: <a href={`mailto:${SUPPORT_EMAIL}`}>{SUPPORT_EMAIL}</a>
				</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Data stored on your device</h2>
			<p>
				Wean Nicotine is local‑first. The app stores your information on your iPhone (and does not require an
				account).
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Usage logs (e.g., “Used a pouch”, “Resisted craving”, with timestamps)</li>
				<li>
					Settings (baseline pouches/day, reduction plan parameters, optional triggers, optional price and
					currency)
				</li>
				<li>Preferences (theme, notification toggles and times)</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>What we do not do</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>No accounts or login</li>
				<li>No ad tracking</li>
				<li>No selling personal data</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Notifications</h2>
			<p>
				If you enable notifications, Wean Nicotine uses local notifications on your device (subject to your iOS
				permissions) for features like daily check‑ins and reminders.
			</p>

			<h2>Third‑party services</h2>
			<p>
				If enabled in the build, Wean Nicotine may use <strong>Sentry</strong> for crash/error reporting to help us
				improve app stability. If used, Sentry may receive error events and basic device/app context
				necessary to diagnose issues (for example: app version, device model, OS version, and a crash stack
				trace). We do not use Sentry for advertising.
			</p>

			<h2>Data retention</h2>
			<p>
				Your data stays on your device unless you delete the app or use “Start Over” inside the app to
				delete local data and return to onboarding.
			</p>

			<h2>Your choices</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Delete data: use “Start Over” inside the app, or delete the app.</li>
				<li>
					Contact us: email <a href={`mailto:${SUPPORT_EMAIL}`}>{SUPPORT_EMAIL}</a>.
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page {
		padding: clamp(44px, 6vw, 84px) 0;
	}

	.prose {
		max-width: 76ch;
	}

	h1 {
		margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);
		font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 44px);
		line-height: 1.1;
		letter-spacing: -0.03em;
	}

	h2 {
		margin: var(--space-xxl) 0 var(--space-sm);
		font-size: 20px;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}

	p,
	li {
		color: var(--text-secondary);
	}

	.muted {
		margin: 0 0 var(--space-xl);
		color: var(--text-tertiary);
	}

	ul {
		margin: var(--space-sm) 0 0;
		padding-left: 18px;
	}

	li {
		margin: 6px 0;
	}
</style>

